description.en: Love Hate Inu launched its mainnet on March 9, 2024 with 100 billion LHINU tokens created at genesis. 90% of the tokens have been allocated to the presale, with the remaining 10% being used for Liquidity, Exchange listings and community rewards. By selling 90% of the tokens, it guarantees no rugpull and creates a strong community foundation. The token has 0% transaction tax.
